Miscellaneous Highlights: The 2024 UEFA Euro match between Hungary and Switzerland will be played on June 15th 2024 at the Rhein Energie at 8:00 (CDT) and will be broadcast live on TV on.
Others: Hungary's squad for the 2024 UEFA Euro includes goalkeepers Balázs Tóth, Dénes Dibusz and Péter Gulácsi, defenders Márton Dárdai, Attila Mocsi, Attila Szalai, Loïc Négo, Gábor Szalai, Zsolt Nagy, Bendegúz Bolla, Botond Balogh, Ádám Lang and Milos Kerkez, midfielders Dominik Szoboszlai, András Schäfer, Roland Sallai, Krisztofer Horváth, László Kleinheisler, Callum Styles, Ádám Nagy and Dániel Gazdag, and forwards Barnabás Varga, Zalán Vancsa and Martin Ádám.

Switzerland's squad for the 2024 UEFA Euro includes goalkeepers David von Ballmoos, Yvon Mvogo and Jonas Omlin, defenders Ricardo Rodríguez, Fabian Schär, Cédric Zesiger, Manuel Akanji, Kevin Mbabu, Nico Elvedi, Eray Cömert, Silvan Widmer and Becir Omeragic, midfielders Remo Freuler, Denis Zakaria, Vincent Sierro, Uran Bislimi, Renato Steffen, Dereck Kutesa, Xherdan Shaqiri, Granit Xhaka, Michel Aebischer and Rubén Vargas, and forwards Noah Okafor, Dan Ndoye and Zeki Amdouni.
